{
  "stem": "5654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, the only-- what worried me, too, is my sister had gone down to-- had- had gone to town with a group of friends.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- I was-- I didn't want to leave, because I didn't want to leave my sister behind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I started to cry and, you know, and-- look, you'll see her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided to walk to the station, which was 2 kilometers away, again, or 4 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the way, my sister was just walking with the others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she didn't even have the time to go back to the-- to our home to pick up her goods.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had to follow us and came with nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything was left there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you children were carrying--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not suitcase.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't carry suitcase, too heavy for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just had whatever we had on our-- just a little bag.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all we had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we took-- we went to Limoges.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that evening, we arrived at the station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put us into upstairs in the station in Limoges.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And about 3 o'clock in the morning, we heard noise.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we looked out outside the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we saw the German assembling Jews from their home and marching them to a camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we watched them from the-- from the top floor, what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The next day, we took a train to the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Somehow, Rabbi Schneerson had paid some non-Jewish people to-- to take us through forests, through field, you know, the way to the-- to the-- to the border.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it took us quite a while to get through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In fact, if you know when--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took a train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we arrived at Annemasse, Annemasse is on the border of Swiss and France.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
